; 06:00 daily — before the 07:25 reminders engine read, so fresh balances feed
; the 07:30 digest + the weekly briefing and the >35d stale-import line stays
; accurate (SPEC §12.2). Cadence is the first tuning knob: if Max/Cal OTP
; re-challenges prove noisy, drop the cards to 2–3×/week, keep the bank daily.
[Unit]
Description=Family inc. finance scraper timer (06:00 Asia/Jerusalem)

[Timer]
OnCalendar=*-*-* 06:00:00
Persistent=true
AccuracySec=1m

[Install]
WantedBy=timers.target
